OL,3,CAwards company leaves businesses
OL,4,C'hundreds of pounds out of pocket'
OL,6,FWelsh businesses say they've been left
OL,7,Fout of pocket after paying hundreds of
OL,8,Fpounds for tickets to industry awards,
OL,9,Fwhich have since been postponed or
OL,10,Fcancelled.
OL,12,FThe event company behind the award
OL,13,Fceremonies is 'Oceanic Awards', who
OL,14,Fhave been accused by ticket holders of
OL,15,Fignoring refund requests, leaving
OL,16,Fbusiness owners frustrated.
OL,18,FComplaints across multiple industries
OL,19,Fsuggest a wider pattern of unpaid
OL,20,Fservices and missing refunds linked to
OL,21,Fthe company.
