OL,6,FKatrina Dimech, a wedding photographer
OL,7,Ffrom Cardiff, is one of many who
OL,8,Fbought tickets to Oceanic Awards'
OL,9,FWelsh Wedding Awards 2025.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Wales' Consumer
OL,12,FAffairs reporter, Kate Lewis, she
OL,13,Fexplained: "I got an email to say I
OL,14,Fhad been nominated, and it's always
OL,15,Fgreat to be recognised for your hard
OL,16,Fwork. So straight away I got in touch
OL,17,Fand said I'd like to buy a ticket."
OL,19,FKatrina paid #96 for a ticket to the
OL,20,Fevent that was initially organised for
OL,21,F12 February.
