OL,6,FHowever, on 10 February, two days
OL,7,Fbefore the planned event, she received
OL,8,Fan email stating it had been postponed
OL,9,Fto May due to 'feedback from
OL,10,Ffinalists'.
OL,12,F"I was a bit annoyed," she said "I
OL,13,Fthought it was a little bit strange."
OL,15,FKatrina was unable to attend the newly
OL,16,Fproposed date and emailed the
OL,17,Forganisers to ask for a refund.
