OL,6,F"I emailed them to say 'Can I get a
OL,7,Frefund as I'm unavailable (on that
OL,8,Fdate)'. I followed that up three or
OL,9,Ffour times, and I was just being
OL,10,Fignored.
OL,12,F"I started to research the company and
OL,13,FI didn't like what I was seeing,
