OL,6,FAlix Jones has been running her bridal
OL,7,Fboutique for the past ten years. She
OL,8,Fis owed around #300 by Oceanic Awards
OL,9,Fafter purchasing tickets for The Welsh
OL,10,FWedding Awards 2025.
OL,12,FShe said: "They rang me asking if I
OL,13,Fwanted tickets as there weren't many
OL,14,Fleft. So I spent #300."
OL,16,F"I've been trying to get a refund
OL,17,Fsince February, and it's just not
OL,18,Fhappening."
