OL,6,FFollowing multiple postponements, Alix
OL,7,Freached out to the company to try to
OL,8,Frecover the money she had paid.
OL,10,F"On their Facebook page, they blocked
OL,11,Fme. (I contacted them) Via emails to
OL,12,Fall the email addresses I could find
OL,13,Fand nobody responded. They just don't
OL,14,Frespond."
OL,16,FAs a small business owner, Alix said
OL,17,Fthe ordeal has left her feeling
OL,18,F"frustrated."
