OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "The awards
OL,7,Fwere only delayed once, two more dates
OL,8,Fwere then provided and a final date
OL,9,Fwas voted for and delivered once we
OL,10,Fhad consensuses from most.
OL,12,F"Enough notice was provided, we have
OL,13,Fall comms in writing that is issued to
OL,14,Ffinalists . Our priority is to make
OL,15,Fsure finalists are able to attend our
OL,16,Fawards, be a part of them and so it is
OL,17,Fimportant they have notice."
OL,19,FHowever, our research shows that on
OL,20,Fthe event's Facebook page, three
OL,21,Fpostponed dates had been advertised.
