OL,6,FKelly said she "dreads to think" how
OL,7,Fmuch money she has lost between
OL,8,Ftickets, hotel accommodation,
OL,9,Ftransport and cancelling clients in
OL,10,Forder to attend.
OL,12,F"Every time you cancel clients,
OL,13,Fthey're going to go somewhere else, so
OL,14,Fyou're going to lose a few customers.
OL,15,FYou're also paying staff for time
OL,16,Fthey're not working, because they've
OL,17,Fbooked (time) off (for the event). So
OL,18,Fit's all these little costs you don't
OL,19,Freally think about.
